# Academy Rules

## Notifications
- Error: critical issues
- Warning: recommendations  
- Success: completed actions
- Info: status updates

## Validation
- Names: min 3 chars
- Email: valid format
- Password: min 8 chars
- Schedule: check conflicts

## UI Colors
- Error: #ef4444
- Warning: #f59e0b
- Success: #10b981
- Info: #3b82f6

